Module LocalizationAPI.main
Package com.github.freddyyj.localizationapi

Class PlayerLocalization

java.lang.Object
com.github.freddyyj.localizationapi.PlayerLocalization
public class PlayerLocalization
extends Object
Player object that has one Player.

To get Player Localization, use fromPlayer(Player). To send or get translated text, use sendMessage(String) or getMessage(String).

FreddyYJ_
